Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是重要的人柱候补
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果身体垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让我头痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.41,0:01:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马可医生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人柱到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:02:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底想让我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你们在做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用这个国家和所有的国民制造巨大的链成阵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了制作贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说对了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过方向对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不协助的话就把那个村子消灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从拉斯多那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们不对那个村子出手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就会协助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助我们毁灭所有国民？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不协助我们让那个村子的人被消灭？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍弃小就能拯救大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微想想就能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这才是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起理论 感情为先
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我杀死的男人也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成那家伙的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就没法出手 让逆转的机会逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太容易钻空子真是太方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}腹中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类居然让你这么费劲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让斯卡逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连库拉多尼也被带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不否认
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有点开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活了六十年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在站在国家的顶点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都如父亲大人预计的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱力克兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有外国来的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连老谋深算的我们也被耍得团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定年轻人的时代已经不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莱德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯 你和人类接触的时间太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了我们是怎样的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那些叛逆的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不向父亲大人报告了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 库拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从宪兵队的情报来分析 已经知道大致的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停住 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别刺激他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的目标是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰芳 要离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在肚子里还养了怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把周围的东西都吞进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然造出了这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链金术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 好不容易抓住的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的生命优先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他记住了我们的脸和名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有放他活着回去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把火焰…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你给我办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 别跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的目标可是大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃进那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 居然在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:06:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德他们还…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能死在这种乱七八糟的战斗里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊·马斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被诱饵骗到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来相当生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点回去 你这没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉坐这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰芳就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我灰溜溜地逃回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下会碍手碍脚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的派不上用场 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个呆子大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 去干你该干的活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队的领袖是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是能放着不管的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队的领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是布拉德雷大总统？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个话题等会再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经满员了吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能把小孩子留在战场上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的战斗对手是军队高层吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得从库拉多尼口中探出情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们留在这里和他战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和是不是小孩子没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次提出作战的是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助我们到这份上 真是谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:08:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个带上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道用法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是杀人的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是保护你们生命的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手不是杀人的手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰芳就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样是会早死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊·马斯坦古在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把拉斯多…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也太恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格也全变了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样才能抓住它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下 库拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说话了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是水蚤草履虫小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来回收库拉多尼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想和小不点打架…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么话题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才两次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第五研究所的地下说了五次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说你忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 那针对某件事情的记忆力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人费神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现马斯坦古了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯多的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞 吞 把他吞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱力克兄弟也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才也感觉到气息了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有几个人？人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和拉斯对砍的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是清国皇帝第十二子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吞他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不能对我们兄弟出手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟 那边拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和拉斯不相上下的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 杰利姆的文章
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被评为班上第一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你写进作文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我能读读吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话就太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲是亚美斯多利斯国的大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个国家拚命干活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲心中所想的一直是这个国家的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大家能和平地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在解决很多问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不论多忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲也不会忘记家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他爱着我 爱着母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我的话 父亲一直都会侧耳倾听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我的愿望 父亲一直会认真地听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 杰利姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺厉害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你的夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们人类没法做到这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你是想被绞死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想被咬死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说被砍死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 那么就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用攻击眼睛这种下三滥的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从小时候就一直在防范暗杀的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯规的技术也不得不学习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能乖乖被抓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要长生不老的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想被折磨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区人类别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别小看人类 人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能吃你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃刚才的细线眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 别妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在 库拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 不能让他把人柱吞进去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 麟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 吐出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把哥哥吐出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 已经吞下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的 这不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有老婆和孩子用过的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开灯太多会让邻居怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我的床上忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去少主身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这身体能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那么直接去司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁这机会区分一下己方和敌方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都这副德行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的伤还没好呢 还想再乱来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大总统也许是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间慢慢等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把孩子们留在战场上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为大人怎么树立榜样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 被大佐当成小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果爱德华君听到了也许会生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是照搬了你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 让我很意外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐居然会走这大胆的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是从周边开始入手而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够理解你和支持你的人 能多一个就多一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点迟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算听从他的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是光荣之门还是魔窟的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉在这里等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能受命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定会回来的 你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 祝您好运
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是罗伊·马斯坦古吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才妻子给我打电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文中将阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到任以来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太过繁忙没能到访
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日又是深夜造访非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说古拉曼那狡猾老头还精神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就11连败了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是12
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你还是下得不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是意识到胜利之后下得太烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说我太天真了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不能完全舍弃感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和雷文一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央的雷文将军？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很优秀 但是对感情很脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经亲自去救负伤的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打乱了阵容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样子有多少棋子都不够用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居 居然如此侮辱我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是因为拯救部下的决心而被中央赏识
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才到中央任职
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可没有被边境的老头说三道四的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一提
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这句话惹您生气的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明将军还是正义之士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都可以和您商量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉曼中将这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被那狐狸摆了一道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到会议的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去会议室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经习惯中央都市了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 虽然想和市民多多交流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市井的传闻也不能忽视
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多数是无足轻重的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡给猫喂食什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死的人出现了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大总统是人造人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 没有搞笑细胞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是古拉曼的部下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那方面没有学到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是那种小传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能成为大家茶余饭后的话题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种人进这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 刚才的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大总统是人造人什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 马斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是人造人所以怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.74,0:21:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 休斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队里不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说军队有危机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是指军队本身有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这里是地狱深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.03,0:22:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找消失的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由于惧怕孤独吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.66,0:24:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即使不见身影也不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.22,0:24:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为坚信着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.71,0:24:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.69,0:24:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第25话 黑暗之门
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.37,0:24:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.30,0:24:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:06.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}纯白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:12.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即将起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:21.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:24.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:30.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不断变化的地图里 搀杂着各种梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:36.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我这微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:43.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那云的彼端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}却受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:49.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}仿佛看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}从天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:53.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}点点雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:56.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}反复的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:59.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}笔直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:01.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:05.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}并不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:06.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不停地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:14.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的残影烙印在两眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:16.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:19.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:22.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:27.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:33.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.26,0:22:37.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:44.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人这样描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:49.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在墙上涂鸦的花也会摇动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:55.54,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.54,0:22:57.82,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漫长的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:01.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去与获取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:08.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:16.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪也好  痛苦也好  都将化为恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:22.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点燃照亮明天的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:27.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举起小手  两个人一起创造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:32.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搜寻星尘与光芒四射的永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:38.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 那天也许还会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:44.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季节依然在不断地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:48.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有点迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.16,0:23:52.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:56.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}请让我维持到永远

